data.description: Welcome to your dream home in a sought-after and desirable neighborhood of Beckett Ridge. This spacious residence boasts 5 beds/2.5 baths, and a partial finished basement, and first floor bedroom. Features updated HVAC, windows, Nest doorbell, Wifi capabilities for battery backup, garage door opener, and thermostat.  New granite kitchen countertop, LVP kitchen flooring, and dining room chandelier to be installed. Enjoy the convenience of golf course, nearby amenities, and a friendly neighborhood atmosphere. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house, your home! Achosa Home Warranty for the first year offered.(see Virtual Tour)
